Title: Koi Nobori
Description: ['Music video directed by Mitsuyuki Ishibashi and animation director Kousuke Sugimoto for the song ', Koi Nobori, ' by JITTERIN\'JINN. The song was originally released as a single in 2001 and was included as a bonus track on their 2007 greatest hits album "8-9-10! (Ver.2)".']
